          "text": "if you are badly afflicted, fly away and do not care, if you are benefited in money or political affairs, do not despise him; for none of these prove to be either certain or permanent, without the least of them having resulted from a brave friendship. for the present law does not lack a way, if it is to be well, it will be enjoyed childishly. For it is a law to us, as on lovers it was working willingly",
